a.xlink:title: A Solver class defines solvers used in analysis.
A Arnoldi class defines a solver using Arnoldi iteration.
The (L-)BFGS class defines a solver using BFGS iteration method.
A FEAST class defines a solver using FEAST iteration.
A DisplacementControl class defines a solver using Newton–Raphson iteration.
A Newton class defines a solver using Newton–Raphson iteration.
A Ramm class defines a solver using Ramm's version of arc–length method.
